            <title>香港 HP 全新 Copilot+ PC 系列發佈，同場加映：新 OMEN MAX 16 高效能電競手提電腦</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/24/hp-copilot-plus-pc/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hp-copilot-plus-pc</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/24/hp-copilot-plus-pc/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 24 Apr 2025 11:06:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304813</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>HP 今日在香港發佈一系列全新 Next Gen AI PC (Copilot+ PC)，主打結合人工智能技術與個人電腦的全新使用體驗，產品陣容針對不同用家需求而設，包括適合自由工作者及流動用家的 OmniBook X Flip 14、OmniBook 7 Aero 13、OmniBook 5 16，以及為電競愛好者打造的 OMEN MAX 16，更有一款適閤家居及辦公室使用的 HP 24 All-in-One Desktop，進一步擴展 AI PC 的應用層面。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05602-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304830" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05602-694x422.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="422" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05602-694x422.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05602-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>HP OmniBook X Flip 14 — 靈活變形，自由工作者的 AI 拍檔</h2><p>HP OmniBook X Flip 14 是一款專為多元工作場景而設的輕薄筆記型電腦，採用鋁鎂合金機身，兼具輕巧與堅固。其 360 度翻轉設計，讓用家隨時轉換筆記型電腦與平板電腦模式，無論是坐在咖啡店回覆電郵，還是在家追劇，都能靈活應用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/07_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/07_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/07_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/07_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg 1059w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC05606" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54473054863/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54473054863_5afa4aa3a1_b.jpg" alt="DSC05606" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05611" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54472786141/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54472786141_77de2532aa_b.jpg" alt="DSC05611" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>處理效能方面，這款電腦可選用 Intel Core Ultra 7 或 AMD Ryzen AI 5 處理器，搭配專屬 AI 引擎，最高達 50 NPU TOPS，支援 AI 圖像處理與數據分析，輕鬆應對日常工作與創作需求。結合 Copilot+PC 的 AI 功能，用家可以透過虛擬助手搜尋資料、管理檔案、強化系統效能，實現更高效率的數位工作模式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05653-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304818" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05653-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05653-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05653-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/05_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304865" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/05_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/05_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/05_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg 1059w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></a></p><p>顯示方面，配備 14 吋 OLED 觸控螢幕，支援高達 3K 解像度及可變刷新率，讓影像畫質細緻流暢，無論觀看影片還是繪圖創作，都能享受視覺盛宴。配合內建的 500 萬像素 AI 高清鏡頭，與 Poly Camera Pro 軟件，讓視訊會議保持最佳畫面質素。重量僅 1.39kg，電池續航力最長可達 14.75 小時，真正實現全天候的流動辦公。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05655-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304819" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05655-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05655-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05655-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05656-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304820" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05656-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05656-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05656-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/04_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304866" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/04_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/04_omnibookxflip_14_-682x580.jpg 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/04_omnibookxflip_14_-scaled.jpg 1059w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></a></p><h2>HP OmniBook 7 Aero 13 — 極致輕盈，滿足隨行工作需求</h2><p>OmniBook 7 Aero 13 主打輕便與效能兼備，機身薄至 16.5mm，重量不到 1kg，專為經常出門在外的用家設計。外型簡約時尚，冰川銀色調搭配鎂鋁合金材質，帶來高質感觸感與堅固機身。</p><p><a title="DSC05670" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471945607/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471945607_7280960889_b.jpg" alt="DSC05670" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05645" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54473056428/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54473056428_282c7aac18_b.jpg" alt="DSC05645" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>搭載 AMD Ryzen AI 7 350 八核心處理器，具備獨立 NPU，支援 50 TOPS AI 運算，能夠提升多工處理效率，應對混合辦公場景。配備 13 吋 2.5K IPS 防眩光螢幕，畫面清晰細膩，超過 90% 屏佔比，無論是文件編輯或簡報展示，都能提供廣闊的視野。</p><p>音效與視訊同樣不容忽視，採用 Poly Studio 音訊技術，支援 DTS:X Ultra，提供沉浸式聽覺體驗；500 萬像素 IR 鏡頭，搭配 Poly Camera Pro，讓視訊會議保持專業。配合 Copilot+PC 及 AI 伴侶，協助用家輕鬆完成日常任務，提升生產力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05638-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304827" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05638-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05638-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05638-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05639-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304828" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05639-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05639-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05639-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/08_omnibook7_14_glac.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/08_omnibook7_14_glac-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/08_omnibook7_14_glac-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/08_omnibook7_14_glac.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>HP OMEN MAX 16 — 久違的 HP 高效能電競手提電腦</h2><p>針對重度玩家與內容創作者，OMEN MAX 16 最高可配備 Intel Core Ultra 9 處理器、NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5090 流動版顯示卡與 64GB DDR5 記憶體，滿足 AAA 遊戲與高效能應用需求。搭載 2.5K OLED 螢幕，並支援 OMEN Gaming Hub 內的「釋放模式」，可將 TPP 推至 250W，釋放硬件潛能。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05629-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304821" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05629-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05629-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05629-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC05666" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471945107/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471945107_1371554847_b.jpg" alt="DSC05666" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05663" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471944997/in/album-72177720325418985/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471944997_b7a37d3311_b.jpg" alt="DSC05663" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>其創新的 OMEN Tempest Cooling Pro 冷卻系統，結合液金屬混合散熱物料 OMEN Cryo Compound 與風扇自動清潔技術，讓效能穩定發揮。機內使用液態金屬散熱技術，而為免物料在機內溢出，HP 採用特別混合物料 OMEN Cryo Compound，將液態金屬結合矽膠，提升粘度，既提供優秀散熱效果，又減低滲漏風險。此外新推 HP 與 Intel 協作的風扇自動清潔技術，會定期反轉風扇轉動方向，以防止灰塵積聚，確保性能表現之餘，亦讓玩家無需頻繁清潔。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11_omenmax16.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11_omenmax16-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11_omenmax16-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11_omenmax16.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10_omenmax16.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304870" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10_omenmax16-673x580.png" alt="" width="673" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10_omenmax16-673x580.png 673w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10_omenmax16.png 1044w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 673px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05630-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304822" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05630-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05630-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05630-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲用戶可設定是否使用自動清理功能（自動清理功能會反向轉動風扇，如用家長期打機，可關掉此功能）</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05631-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304823" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05631-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05631-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05631-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05632-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304824" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05632-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05632-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05632-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05633-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304825" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05633-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05633-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05633-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05634-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304826" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05634-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05634-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05634-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>外觀設計則配備 RGB 燈效，並支援個性化調校，為玩家打造獨一無二的沉浸式體驗。</p><p><a title="DSC05624" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471944032/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471944032_692c7e5bee_b.jpg" alt="DSC05624" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05628" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54471944162/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54471944162_d01a26ac5f_b.jpg" alt="DSC05628" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2></h2><h2>HP OmniBook 5 16 — 可靠耐用，兼顧工作與娛樂</h2><p>對於追求穩定效能和實用性的人士，OmniBook 5 16 是理想之選。搭載 AMD Ryzen AI 5 處理器，配備高達 50 TOPS AI 引擎，內建 16GB LPDDR5x 記憶體，兼具 AI 加速與多工效能，讓日常工作更順暢。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/09_omnibook5_16_skyb.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/09_omnibook5_16_skyb-682x580.png" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/09_omnibook5_16_skyb-682x580.png 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/09_omnibook5_16_skyb.png 1059w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></a><a title="DSC05614" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54472786221/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54472786221_b5b6ab757a_b.jpg" alt="DSC05614" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC05618" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54472985069/in/album-72177720325418985" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54472985069_72fb711ecf_b.jpg" alt="DSC05618" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>採用 16 吋 2K WUXGA 觸控螢幕，提供更大顯示空間，輕鬆處理多個視窗或享受影音娛樂。鋁金屬機身配以天空藍色調，提升質感。搭載 True Vision 1080p FHD IR 視訊鏡頭，支援私隱護蓋，保障個人私隱。</p><h2>HP 24 All-in-One Desktop — 簡潔一體，適閤家居與辦公</h2><p>HP 24 All-in-One Desktop 配備 AMD Ryzen 5 AI 340 處理器，為家居與辦公環境提供高效、簡潔的使用體驗。一體化設計節省空間，螢幕與主機合而為一，適合會議、文書處理或多媒體娛樂。</p><h2>HP 全新系列電腦香港售價</h2><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="top">產品</td><td valign="top">售價</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP OmniBook X Flip 14</td><td valign="top">由 HK$10,999 起</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP OmniBook 7 Aero 13</td><td valign="top">由 HK$8,999 起</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP OmniBook 5 16</td><td valign="top">由 HK$7,999 起</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP OMEN MAX 16</td><td valign="top">由 HK$22,999 起</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">HP 24 All-in-One Desktop PC</td><td valign="top">由 HK$8,999 起</td></tr></tbody></table><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/18_omenmax16-scaled.jpg"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13_omnibookxflip14-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13_omnibookxflip14-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13_omnibookxflip14-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13_omnibookxflip14-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/24/hp-copilot-plus-pc/notebook/">香港 HP 全新 Copilot+ PC 系列發佈，同場加映：新 OMEN MAX 16 高效能電競手提電腦</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
